title: Baskilla
body:
Etymology

Common Name: Baskilla

Domathundic: Baðkilla

Éman: Baskilla


The five Baskiþa are:

  • Desomnï (Desomnair) - Traits: Destructive/Smug
  • Kusümë (Kusoomer) - Traits: Sinister/Malificent
  • Põmeç (Poimech) - Traits: Conflicted/Pensive
  • Đeşema (Thesema) - Traits: Cunning/Jovial
  • Eþïrö (Ethairor) - Traits: Argumentative/Wreckless
preface: Edrenaen's five Baðkilla were created to infiltrate the ranks of Urúneen's beasts (namely the Hagalisk and the Gargoyles).
